&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( english : chance ) is a 2016 indian malayalam-language action drama film written and directed by jeethu joseph . the film stars prithviraj sukumaran , neeraj madhav , divya pillai and debutant &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; pavithran in the lead roles . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; handled the cinematography . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; revolves around a demolition expert who teams up with his fiancee and friend to avenge the deaths of their family members from the ceo of a pharmaceutical company who got them killed . the film released on 8 september 2016 . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; grossed more than 15 crores from kerala boxoffice and 30 cr from worldwide boxoffice thereby becoming a super hit .